            <div class="stat">
              <span class="number">500+</span>
              <span class="label">iPhones Repaired</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <span class="number">30 min</span>
              <span class="label">Average Repair</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <span class="number">4.9★</span>
              <span class="label">Google Rating</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Common iPhone Problems -->
  <section class="common-problems">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">iPhone Problems We Fix in Dallas</h2>
      <div class="problems-grid">
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg role="img" aria-label="Cracked iPhone screen repair icon" width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <path d="m9 9 5 5"/>
              <path d="m15 9-5 5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Cracked Screen</h3>
          <p>Most common repair - fixed in 30 minutes with lifetime warranty on workmanship and certified technicians. We also repair <a href="/samsung-repair-fort-worth" title="Samsung screen repair">Samsung screens</a> and offer <a href="/screen-replacement" title="All device screen repairs">screen replacement for all devices</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg role="img" aria-label="iPhone battery replacement icon" width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="1" y="6" width="18" height="10" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <line x1="22" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Battery Replacement</h3>
          <p>Phone dying fast? Professional new battery installation with genuine capacity cells and warranty coverage. Also servicing <a href="/mac-troubleshooting-dfw" title="Mac battery service">MacBook batteries</a> and <a href="/windows-troubleshooting-dfw" title="Laptop battery replacement">Windows laptop batteries</a>.</p>
