            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Water Damage</h3>
          <p>Dropped in water? We offer <a href="/emergency-phone-repair" title="Emergency phone repair service">emergency water damage recovery services</a>. Also servicing <a href="/samsung-repair-fort-worth" title="Samsung repair service in Fort Worth">Samsung devices</a> and all <a href="/screen-replacement" title="Professional screen replacement service">screen replacement</a> needs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg role="img" aria-label="iPhone charging port repair icon" width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="m15 2 3 3.3a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.4L15 10"/>
              <path d="M9 22l-3-3.3a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.4L9 14"/>
              <path d="M20 14h-2"/>
              <path d="M20 10h-2"/>
              <path d="M7 10H4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Charging Issues</h3>
          <p>Won't charge? Professional Lightning port replacement and charging IC repair with same-day service. We fix charging issues on all devices including <a href="/samsung-repair-fort-worth" title="Samsung charging repair">Samsung Galaxy</a> phones.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg role="img" aria-label="iPhone camera repair icon" width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M23 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Camera Repair</h3>
          <p>Blurry photos? Cracked lens? Professional front and back camera replacements with quality restoration. Camera repairs available for all <a href="/services" title="All repair services">mobile devices</a>.</p>
