              <path d="m19.07 4.93-1.41 1.41A8 8 0 0 1 19.07 19.07l1.41 1.41A10 10 0 0 0 19.07 4.93z"/>
              <path d="m15.54 8.46-1.41 1.41A4 4 0 0 1 15.54 15.54l1.41 1.41A6 6 0 0 0 15.54 8.46z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Speaker/Mic Issues</h3>
          <p>Can't hear or be heard? Professional speaker and microphone repairs with certified technicians. Audio repairs for <a href="/emergency-phone-repair" title="Emergency audio repairs">urgent situations</a> available.</p>
