          <h3>Schedule Service</h3>
          <p>We come to your location in Dallas at your convenience with mobile service</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">3</span>
          <h3>Expert Repair</h3>
          <p>30-minute professional repair while you wait or work with warranty coverage</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">4</span>
          <h3>Quality Check</h3>
          <p>Thorough testing and 90-day warranty on all parts and labor</p>
